!/w gm &{template:default}{& define ([AmmoDie]  ?{What is your current ammo die value?|1d12|1d10|1d6|1d4|1}) ([RollResult] [[?{What is your current ammo die value?}]]) ([ReducedTo] {& if AmmoDie ~ 'd12'}d10{& elseif AmmoDie ~ 'd10'}d8{& elseif AmmoDie ~ 'd8'}d6{& elseif AmmoDie ~ 'd6'}d4{& elseif AmmoDie ~ 'd4'}1{& elseif AmmoDie ~ '1'}0{& else }0{& end})}{{name=Ammo Check (AmmoDie)}}{{Result=RollResult}}{&if RollResult < 3}{{Ammo Lost! Decrease your ammo die to=ReducedTo}}{& else}{{Yer Ammo's Good}}{& end}{&simple}